judgment_text:
IN THE HIGH COURT OF BOMBAY AT PANAJI STAMP NO. 103 OF 2007 IN COMPANY PETITION NO. 3 OF 1988 M/s. West Coast Foundaries Pvt. Ltd. ...... Petitioners Official Liquidator present in person. CORAM: N. A. BRITTO, J. DATE: th January, 2007

. P.C. The matter is being adjourned from time to time for the purpose of filing the Dissolution Report from 04.08.2006. The Official Liquidator has now filed an application dated 12.01.2007, stating that certain procedures are required to be followed before the Dissolution Report is filed for which the Official Liquidator required permission from this Court to spend certain amounts. The Official Liquidator has prayed that an amount of Rs.5,255/- towards publication and Rs.2,000/- towards postage, Court fees, etc, is required to be spent. The Official Liquidator is permitted to spend the said sum of Rs.5,255/- and Rs.2,000/-, as aforesaid. The Official Liquidator assures the Court that the certified list of Creditors will be filed within a period of two and half months. S.O. after 11 weeks. Application under Stamp No. 103/2007, shall stand disposed of. N. A. BRITTO, J. arp/*
